high_descs: Turn left, go forward, go around the counter to the left and keep going forward, at the fridge turn left, go forward to the counter.
Take the knife from the counter.
Turn left, go forward and around the counter to the left, go forward, before reaching the round table turn right, go forward to the wall, turn left to the round white table.
Cut the left lettuce on the table into slices.
Turn left, go forward, turn left after passing the end of the counter to the left, go forward, turn right at the fridge, go to the fridge.
Put the knife to the right of the mug in the fridge.
Turn right, go forward, turn right after passing the end of the counter, go forward to the wall, turn left to face the round white table.
Take a slice of lettuce from the table.
Turn left, go forward, turn left after passing the end of the counter to the left, go forward, turn right at the fridge, go to the fridge.
Chill the lettuce in the fridge to the right of the knife. Take the lettuce from the fridge.
Turn right, go forward, turn right after passing the end of the counter, go forward to the wall, turn left to face the round white table.
Put the lettuce between the closest small knife and large knife on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of lettuce on a table.

high_descs: Go into the kitchen and to the counter adjacent to the dishwasher.
Pick up the knife paring knife on the counter top.
Turn around and go to the white round table on the opposite side of the kitchen.
Slice the green bell pepper on the table.
Turn around and go around the counter to the refrigerator.
Place the paring knife on the middle shelf in the refrigerator.
Turn around and go back to the white round table.
Pick up the lettuce on the table.
Turn around and go back to the refrigerator.
Chill the lettuce in the refrigerator and take it out.
Turn right and take the lettuce back to the white table.
Place the lettuce on the table between the paring knife and the chef's knife.
anns.task_desc: Place chilled lettuce on the table.

slice the lettuce head
turn around towards the refrigerator
drop the knife inside the refrigerator
turn right and head for the table

drop the lettuce to cool and then take it out
